social_posts.post_text: E V E N T  C O V E R A G E: an exclusive event with the Pirates of @marriottsgrandevista Copa Loca Bar & Grill (Orlando, FL) and @theamericanmermaid_ 🧜🏼‍♀️ 🏴‍☠️ we had the opportunity to snap a few shots for them and here they are! Thank you photographer @mannyoquendo

🧜‍♀️✨ Happy Magical Mermaid Moments! ✨🧜‍♀️

I am beyond thrilled to share some exciting news with all of you! 🌟🎥🌊 As you know, I've always been captivated by the mystical world of merpeople, and now I have the incredible opportunity to take you behind the scenes of the enchanting Merpeople documentary on Netflix! 🎬🌍

But that's not all! This magical journey is taking place aboard the extraordinary @virginvoyages cruise, where we're immersing ourselves in the captivating world of mermaids and setting a Guinness World Record! 🌟📚🚢 Can you believe it? It's a once-in-a-lifetime experience, and I'm thrilled to be a part of it.

From exploring breathtaking underwater kingdoms to witnessing the mesmerizing beauty of these extraordinary creatures, this documentary will transport you to a realm you've only dreamt of. 🌊🎥✨

And the excitement doesn't end there! The Little Mermaid is making its grand debut this week, and what better way to celebrate than by diving deep into the enchanting lore of mermaids? 🧜‍♀️🌹✨

So, grab your popcorn, settle in, and get ready for an extraordinary adventure. Join me on this incredible journey as we uncover the secrets of the sea and unravel the captivating stories of merpeople.

Let's make this week a celebration of all things magical, as we dive into the depths of the ocean and embrace the wonder that lies beneath the waves. 🌊🎉✨

Remember to tune in to the Merpeople documentary on Netflix and join us in creating history as we set a Guinness World Record aboard the @virginvoyages cruise! It's time to make some unforgettable memories together!
